flowchart TD
    A[Start: EDA findings and hypotheses] --> B[Re-target methods to each hypothesis]
    B --> C[Quantify effect size and uncertainty]
    C --> D[Choose rigorous method per question]
    D --> E[Decompose changes by segment, time, and driver]
    E --> F[Check temporal dynamics and inflection points]
    F --> G[Test alternative drivers]
    G --> H[Assess confidence and limitations]
    H --> I[Write deep-analysis.md with quantified answers]
    I --> J[Save charts and query CSV outputs]
    J --> K[Checkpoint: proceed to Synthesis?]
